        if runnerSpeed >= 4 then
            return [[You unfold the scouting report and scan the notes on the catcher:

"Pop time to second: 2.1 seconds. Below average arm. Release is slow. Steal opportunities are there if you get a good jump."

A steal of second could work.]]
        else
            return [[You unfold the scouting report and scan the notes:

"Pitcher has a quick slide step. Tough to steal on. Best bet is to stay put and let your batter put the ball in play."

Staying put and trusting your hitter is the safer call.]]
        end
    elseif currentBase == "second" then
        if batterContact >= 4 or batterPower >= 4 then
            return [[You unfold the scouting report and check the matchup notes:

"This batter has crushed this pitcher in the past. Let him cook."

Your hitter can drive you in. Stay patient.]]
        else
            return [[You unfold the scouting report and find a note circled in red:

"Pitcher ignores runners at 2B. Has not thrown over once all game."

A steal of third might catch them completely off guard.]]
        end
    else
        if batterBunting >= 3 then
            return [[You unfold the scouting report and read the defensive alignment:

"3B playing deep, back on the grass. Vulnerable to the squeeze play."

A squeeze bunt could catch the defense flat-footed.]]
        else
