            short .. " swings for the fences but gets under it. A high fly ball to center field. The outfielder barely has to move. Caught.",
            short .. " muscles the ball into the air, but it doesn't have the distance. The left fielder settles under it and makes the catch.",
            short .. " drives one deep to right, but the wind knocks it down. The outfielder backs up and hauls it in at the track.",
