            "You break for second on the first move! The catcher pops up and throws, but the ball sails into center field! You're in at second standing up!",
            "The pitch is low and you explode out of your crouch! The catcher blocks it cleanly but you're already halfway there. The throw comes -- you slide -- SAFE at second!",
